<item>
            <title>[LU-4441] sanity test_60a: Module llog_test is in use</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-4441</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;This issue was created by maloo for Bob Glossman &amp;lt;bob.glossman@intel.com&amp;gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;This issue relates to the following test suite run: &lt;a href=&quot;http://maloo.whamcloud.com/test_sets/b44af13a-761f-11e3-a7a8-52540035b04c&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;http://maloo.whamcloud.com/test_sets/b44af13a-761f-11e3-a7a8-52540035b04c&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Even though maloo reports a 0% failure, search on subtest 60a of sanity shows a bunch of FAILs&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;The sub-test test_60a failed with the following error:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;blockquote&gt;
&lt;p&gt;wtm-20vm3: ERROR: Module llog_test is in use&lt;br/&gt;
test_60a failed with 3&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/blockquote&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Info required for matching: sanity 60a&lt;/p&gt;</description>
